  "detailed_description": "<h1>Reviews Plaque</h1><p><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1286990/extras/8417f51d4f8f567cea370a782c1f2d37.avif?t=1764865767\" width=1560 height=878 /></span></p><br><h1>Trench Raider Pack</h1><p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Battle through the trenches with 3 additional uniforms to choose from in the Trench Raider Pack, containing:</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >• Elite Trench Raider</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >• Pilot</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >• English Tommy</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1286990/extras/944166a15bb07679631aab1b01eff77b.avif?t=1764865767\" width=1200 height=550 /></span></p></p><br><h1>About the Game</h1><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1286990/extras/6aafb855716ed70c2069bcaff7472e94.poster.avif?t=1764865767\" width=1170 height=244 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1286990/extras/6aafb855716ed70c2069bcaff7472e94.webm?t=1764865767\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1286990/extras/6aafb855716ed70c2069bcaff7472e94.mp4?t=1764865767\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><strong>CONSCRIPT i</strong>s a top-down survival horror experience inspired by genre classics—blending strategic resource management, methodical combat, and suffocating atmosphere into a grim, historically grounded nightmare.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1286990/extras/19053e3db3a4b23c60f8388011a5b6bf.poster.avif?t=1764865767\" width=1170 height=244 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1286990/extras/19053e3db3a4b23c60f8388011a5b6bf.webm?t=1764865767\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1286990/extras/19053e3db3a4b23c60f8388011a5b6bf.mp4?t=1764865767\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><strong>The Battle of Verdun, 1916. </strong>World War I’s bloodiest conflict rages as the German Army drives deep into France.<br><br>Your younger brother has vanished amid the chaos.<br><br>Dive into the madness of war. Engage in brutal combat against hostile troops, manage scarce supplies, and solve complex environmental puzzles as you explore collapsed trench lines, infiltrate occupied forts, and cross no man's land in a desperate search for your lost kin.<br><br><strong>Can you find the flesh and blood you’ve lost—and ensure a home goes unbroken?</strong><br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1286990/extras/b2340f15fda8a1f587a3c77950085ad2.avif?t=1764865767\" width=1175 height=148 /></span><br><br><strong>True Classic Survival Horror</strong><br>Limited ammunition. Fragile health. Relentless tension. Every encounter demands resolve.<br><br><strong>Tailor the Terror</strong><br>Play with modern comforts such as checkpoints, unlimited saving, and an expanded inventory—or commit to the strict limitations of classic survival horror.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1286990/extras/452fa56956ca508e581a5daa28f40082.avif?t=1764865767\" width=1178 height=145 /></span><br><br><strong>A Historically Grounded Nightmare</strong><br>Survive the Battle of Verdun through evocative pixel art and oppressive soundscapes that capture the brutality of one of history’s darkest battles.<br><br><strong>War-Torn Labyrinths</strong><br>Explore intertwining trenches, towns, forts, and battlefields that demand careful route planning, inventory management, and puzzle-solving.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1286990/extras/11375e71b991b926d64314bdcb4afcf5.avif?t=1764865767\" width=1177 height=144 /></span><br><br><strong>Intense, Visceral Combat</strong><br>Engage enemy combatants with authentic WWI melee weapons and firearms in desperate, claustrophobic encounters.<br><br><strong>Return for Another Tour</strong><br>Highly replay value with a full range of difficulties, multiple endings, unlockable costumes, rankings, and bonus weapons.<br>",
  "about_the_game": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1286990/extras/6aafb855716ed70c2069bcaff7472e94.poster.avif?t=1764865767\" width=1170 height=244 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1286990/extras/6aafb855716ed70c2069bcaff7472e94.webm?t=1764865767\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1286990/extras/6aafb855716ed70c2069bcaff7472e94.mp4?t=1764865767\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><strong>CONSCRIPT i</strong>s a top-down survival horror experience inspired by genre classics—blending strategic resource management, methodical combat, and suffocating atmosphere into a grim, historically grounded nightmare.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1286990/extras/19053e3db3a4b23c60f8388011a5b6bf.poster.avif?t=1764865767\" width=1170 height=244 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1286990/extras/19053e3db3a4b23c60f8388011a5b6bf.webm?t=1764865767\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1286990/extras/19053e3db3a4b23c60f8388011a5b6bf.mp4?t=1764865767\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><strong>The Battle of Verdun, 1916. </strong>World War I’s bloodiest conflict rages as the German Army drives deep into France.<br><br>Your younger brother has vanished amid the chaos.<br><br>Dive into the madness of war. Engage in brutal combat against hostile troops, manage scarce supplies, and solve complex environmental puzzles as you explore collapsed trench lines, infiltrate occupied forts, and cross no man's land in a desperate search for your lost kin.<br><br><strong>Can you find the flesh and blood you’ve lost—and ensure a home goes unbroken?</strong><br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1286990/extras/b2340f15fda8a1f587a3c77950085ad2.avif?t=1764865767\" width=1175 height=148 /></span><br><br><strong>True Classic Survival Horror</strong><br>Limited ammunition. Fragile health. Relentless tension. Every encounter demands resolve.<br><br><strong>Tailor the Terror</strong><br>Play with modern comforts such as checkpoints, unlimited saving, and an expanded inventory—or commit to the strict limitations of classic survival horror.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1286990/extras/452fa56956ca508e581a5daa28f40082.avif?t=1764865767\" width=1178 height=145 /></span><br><br><strong>A Historically Grounded Nightmare</strong><br>Survive the Battle of Verdun through evocative pixel art and oppressive soundscapes that capture the brutality of one of history’s darkest battles.<br><br><strong>War-Torn Labyrinths</strong><br>Explore intertwining trenches, towns, forts, and battlefields that demand careful route planning, inventory management, and puzzle-solving.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1286990/extras/11375e71b991b926d64314bdcb4afcf5.avif?t=1764865767\" width=1177 height=144 /></span><br><br><strong>Intense, Visceral Combat</strong><br>Engage enemy combatants with authentic WWI melee weapons and firearms in desperate, claustrophobic encounters.<br><br><strong>Return for Another Tour</strong><br>Highly replay value with a full range of difficulties, multiple endings, unlockable costumes, rankings, and bonus weapons.<br>",
